## interrupts-extended

Specifies the interrupt(s) generated by the device in extended form, allowing each interrupt to reference a different interrupt controller.

```dts
/* arch/arm64/boot/dts/allwinner/sun50i-h6.dtsi */
mmc0: mmc@4020000 {
    interrupts-extended = <&gic GIC_SPI 35 IRQ_TYPE_LEVEL_HIGH>,
                          <&r_intc 6 IRQ_TYPE_LEVEL_HIGH>;
};
```
